listing.description:
Canal side B&B in the heart of the city centre in Amsterdam. Very central with walking distance of everything interesting!
Located next to the Opera, Rembrandhouse, antique market and Hermitage museum and walking distance to the all of interesting!

Minimum stay is 3 nights, 2 nights are possible in case of last minute, in the low season (1 Nov- 1 March) and exactly between 2 bookings.

review.comments: The B&B had the perfect location which meant we couldn't walk to nearly every tourist attraction. The breakfast in the morning was lovely. Judith was very fast in replying to my messages and helping us with anything we needed. Thank you!
